{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[G]  Oh, who knows how long this will last
[C]  Now we've come so far, so fast
[G]  But somewhere back there in the dust
That[C]  same small town in each[D]  of us
[G]  I need to remember this
[C]  So baby, give me just one kiss
[G]  And let me take a long last look
Be[Em]fore we say[C]  goodbye[D]
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus: Chorus}
Jus [G]lay your head[D]  back on[C]  the ground
And [Em]let your hair[Bm]  fall all[Am]   around[C]  me
[G]Offer up[D]  your best[C]  defense
[Em]This is the end[Bm]
[Am]    [C]This is the end[D]  of the [G]innocence
{end_of_chorus}

